461
00:35:46,345 --> 00:35:49,380
In the starting gate,
Andrea Meade Lawrence,

462
00:35:49,381 --> 00:35:51,686
Number six, to the gate,
please ...wearing number six.

463
00:35:52,584 --> 00:35:53,585
Go, Andy.

464
00:35:54,553 --> 00:35:55,821
Yes, we're ready.

