00:36:26,685 --> 00:36:29,321
That's gonna be hard to beat.
She's way ahead of the field.

468
00:36:44,470 --> 00:36:47,973
Next up,
number 89, Jill Kinmont.

469
00:36:51,377 --> 00:36:53,344
You can win the race.

470
00:36:53,345 --> 00:36:55,513
You're gonna win all right?

471
00:36:55,514 --> 00:36:58,416
Just be smooth, and use your head,
and hang onto that mountain. All right?

472
00:36:58,417 --> 00:37:00,017
Officials ready? Ready.

