00:39:39,077 --> 00:39:40,478
Okay, on the count of three

503
00:39:40,479 --> 00:39:41,879
we'll all lift very slowly.

504
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:42,980
Ready?

505
00:39:42,981 --> 00:39:45,016
One, two, three.

506
00:39:51,890 --> 00:39:53,592
There you go.
Keep her head from moving.

507
00:40:08,940 --> 00:40:11,843
Ready? One, two, three.

508
00:40:14,746 --> 00:40:16,581
Here we go.

509
00:40:16,582 --> 00:40:18,483
Be careful now.

510
00:40:18,484 --> 00:40:20,418
Try and keep it level. Easy.

511
00:41:18,009 --> 00:41:19,244
Take it easy.

512
00:41:27,018 --> 00:41:28,186
Take it easy.

513
00:41:46,271 --> 00:41:48,073
Move back away from her.

514
00:41:49,708 --> 00:41:51,142
Driver, let's go.

515
00:42:20,806 --> 00:42:23,240
Driver, how long
do you think it'll be?

516
00:42:23,241 --> 00:42:24,842
Looks like it's
backed up for miles,

517
00:42:24,843 --> 00:42:25,943
it could take hours.

518
00:42:25,944 --> 00:42:26,912
She won't make it.

519
00:42:26,913 --> 00:42:30,080
Dave... I... I'm not gonna die.

520
00:42:30,081 --> 00:42:31,549
Now, you listen to me,

521
00:42:33,585 --> 00:42:34,953
this is Jill Kinmont.

522
00:42:37,989 --> 00:42:40,692
